{"tid":1889241,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［Repost］我想知道臨時政府會有幾多人support","createTime":"2020-02-20T14:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T03:17:19.000Z","uid":223428,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c50520763ca3a34b01860a31bc82b4bc4f0ee0c4","tid":1889241,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"大家都話起臨時政府是開玩笑，沒有民意認受性；但是，沒有經過調查，我地點知冇呢？<br />\n<br />\n個個都話想，個個都話唔得，是因為我們不知道情況。會唔會到頭來七百萬人十卜，但個個都話冇民意呢？就算只是ff，認真地玩不行嗎？<br />\n<br />\n正如我之前講過，議員睇唔到民意可能會唔做野，而Sample size 太細又唔準確，對我呢ｄ笨蛋特別棘手，但HKvote同tg 的用家唔夠連登呢ｄ平台廣泛，所以我用Google form開多次，在此向大家道歉，要阻大家一兩分鐘到時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">同時，為了降低同溫層效應帶來的誤差（個男女比例明顯和香港實況不符，可見之。），我希望大家可以放上facebook同ig 去傳（再勇武ｄ的可以放上港人港地之類的深藍谷，費時他們嘈偽中立，同時加強趣味和代表性）</span>，令已經放上ig的人不至於有被人mark實的危機。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n問卷在此：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/MPT11Gs4cg5kzbt78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FMPT11Gs4cg5kzbt78&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=bf9ab235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/MPT11Gs4cg5kzbt78</a>"},{"pid":"a7ce984e950786ccb1703a041a35fca2282ddb74","tid":1889241,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"已經爆左500"},{"pid":"8787515a1b207b57391d3fb2e7e2cbda602f96de","tid":1889241,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"可以破到2000就好啦"},{"pid":"4f0c277b9ba926dfd017cc3a3bb172863016991b","tid":1889241,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"主權在民，香港獨立"},{"pid":"58db07a1d9388070c7701ebedd4ee8f1d67f7efe","tid":1889241,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"8788891c43ce9642599fc35d0da33aab7488edb8","tid":1889241,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy